articles.title: US facing obstacles getting aid delivered to Gaza after finishing pier construction - CNN
articles.description: Desperately needed humanitarian aid for Palestinians in Gaza will at least for the next few days remain sitting off the coast of Gaza on an American Navy cargo ship, as the US continues to face obstacles to getting a floating pier in place and operational in …
